<lb n="0519b23" ed="T"/><cb:div type="xu"><cb:mulu level="1" type="序">新譯仁王般若經陀羅尼念誦軌儀序</cb:mulu><head><note n="0519027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本，此序宋元明甲四本俱無之</note>新譯仁王般若經陀羅尼念誦軌
<lb n="0519b24" ed="T"/>儀序</head>
<lb n="0519b25" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0519b26" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="author">大興善寺翻經沙門慧靈述</byline>
<lb n="0519b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0519b2701">我皇帝聖德廣運仁育群品。亦既纂曆吹大
<lb n="0519b28" ed="T"/>法螺。刊梵言之輕重。警迷徒之耳目。偉矣
<lb n="0519b29" ed="T"/>哉。迺辟興善寺大廣智三藏不空。與義學沙
<pb n="0519c" xml:id="T19.0995.0519c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0519c01" ed="T"/>門良賁等一十四人。開府魚朝恩翰林學士
<lb n="0519c02" ed="T"/>常袞等。去歲夏四月。於南桃園再譯斯經。秋
<lb n="0519c03" ed="T"/>九月詔資聖西明。百座敷闡。下紫微而五雲
<lb n="0519c04" ed="T"/>抱出。經長衢而萬姓作禮。阡郭充滿猶墻堵
<lb n="0519c05" ed="T"/>焉。稽緇衣覽青史。自摩騰入漢僧會遊矣。瑞
<lb n="0519c06" ed="T"/>法之來莫與京者。經云若未來世有諸國王。
<lb n="0519c07" ed="T"/>建立正法護三寶者。我令五方菩薩往護其
<lb n="0519c08" ed="T"/>國令無災難。又云五菩薩自於佛前發弘誓
<lb n="0519c09" ed="T"/>言。我有陀羅尼能加持擁護。是一切佛本所
<lb n="0519c10" ed="T"/>修行速疾之門。若人得聞一經於耳。所有罪
<lb n="0519c11" ed="T"/>障悉皆消滅況復習誦而令通利。佛即讚言
<lb n="0519c12" ed="T"/>若誦持此陀羅尼者。我及十方諸佛悉常擁
<lb n="0519c13" ed="T"/>護。諸惡鬼神敬之如佛。不久當得阿耨菩提。
<lb n="0519c14" ed="T"/>則知此陀羅尼。字母之根底眾瑜伽之藪澤。
<lb n="0519c15" ed="T"/>如彼水木歸其本源。故菩薩演之王者建之。
<lb n="0519c16" ed="T"/>黎人念之諸佛讚之。俾爾昌而熾俾爾福而
<lb n="0519c17" ed="T"/>利。於可以見聖人之心。其益既弘其軌亦妙。
<lb n="0519c18" ed="T"/>苟于誠不克曷降之以嘉。三藏是以譯具多
<lb n="0519c19" ed="T"/>之文。良賁法師乃受從簡素。始夫處所方便
<lb n="0519c20" ed="T"/>終其觀行儀則。修為十門第以位次。一一昭
<lb n="0519c21" ed="T"/>著庶無懵焉。凡我道俗將保厥躬遂求願。踐
<lb n="0519c22" ed="T"/>菩提之路登仁壽之域者。何莫由斯之道哉。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0520a" xml:id="T19.0995.0520a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0520a01" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0520a02" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead>仁王般若念誦法<note n="0520001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一卷〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一卷【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520001"><lem wit="【大】">一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0520a03" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0520a04" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0520002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（開府…門）四十一字＝（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十一字【宋】【元】，（唐三藏沙門大廣智）八字【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…門）四十一字【大】，大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智【宋】【元】，唐三藏沙門大廣智【明】【甲】</note><app cb:word-count="41" n="0520002"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿
<lb n="0520a05" ed="T"/>肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司
<lb n="0520a06" ed="T"/>空謚大鑒正號大廣智大興善
<lb n="0520a07" ed="T"/>寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">唐三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0520a08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><p xml:id="pT19p0520a0801">爾時佛告波斯匿王。今為王說仁王護國般
<lb n="0520a09" ed="T"/>若波羅蜜多持明之法。王當諦受一心善聽。
<lb n="0520a10" ed="T"/>先明入道場儀軌。</p>
<lb n="0520a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520a1101">若諸仁王為求息災。先須沐浴著新淨衣。若
<lb n="0520a12" ed="T"/><note n="0520003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔法〕－【三】</note><note n="0520003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0520003"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>行王者受近住戒。應起殷重大乘之心。欲
<lb n="0520a13" ed="T"/>求成就不惜身命。於無邊有情廣起悲願濟
<lb n="0520a14" ed="T"/>度之心能如是者速得成就。入道場已五體
<lb n="0520a15" ed="T"/>投地。遍禮法界一切三寶右膝著地懺悔三
<lb n="0520a16" ed="T"/>業一切罪障。勸十方佛轉正法輪。請諸如來
<lb n="0520a17" ed="T"/>久住於世。隨喜三乘所修福智。以我某甲所
<lb n="0520a18" ed="T"/>修功德。悉皆迴向無上菩提。願共法界一切
<lb n="0520a19" ed="T"/>有情。所求悉地速得滿足。次結<note n="0520004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">跏＝加【宋】【元】＊</note><note n="0520004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->跏【大】＊，加【宋】【元】＊</note><app n="0520004"><lem wit="【大】">跏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">加</rdg></app>趺坐。如
<lb n="0520a20" ed="T"/>其闕緣不得澡浴。二手塗香發慇重心。結清
<lb n="0520a21" ed="T"/>淨印。兩手當心虛心合掌如未敷蓮華誦真
<lb n="0520a22" ed="T"/>言<note n="0520005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曰〕－【元】</note><note n="0520005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曰【大】，〔－〕【元】</note><app n="0520005"><lem wit="【大】">曰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0520a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520a2301" cb:type="dharani"><note n="0520006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">唵＋（一）細註【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0520006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵【大】＊，唵(一)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>婆<note place="inline">引</note>嚩輸<note place="inline"><note n="0520007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">入＋（聲）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】，入聲【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520007"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">入聲</rdg></app></note>鐸<note place="inline"><note n="0520008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（二）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0520008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】＊，引二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0520008"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引二</rdg></app></note>薩嚩達磨<note n="0520009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（上三）【宋】【元】，引＝上聲聲三【明】，上聲引三【甲】</note><note n="0520009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，引上三【宋】【元】，上聲聲三【明】，上聲引三【甲】</note><app n="0520009"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><note place="inline">引上三</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><note place="inline">上聲聲三</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">上聲引三</note></rdg></app>
<lb n="0520a24" ed="T"/>娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0520010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婆＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】，婆(引)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520010"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">婆<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>嚩輸度<note n="0520011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撼＝憾四【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">撼【大】，憾四【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520011"><lem wit="【大】">撼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">憾四</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0520a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520a2501">誦此真言三遍。正誦之時運心廣布。一切諸
<lb n="0520a26" ed="T"/>法本來清淨。是故我身亦悉清淨。即閉目運
<lb n="0520a27" ed="T"/>想。遍滿虛空一切諸佛菩薩道場眾會。執持
<lb n="0520a28" ed="T"/>種種上妙香花。三業至誠頭面禮敬。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520a29" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="1" type="其他">1 結佛部三昧耶印</cb:mulu><head>第一結佛部三昧耶印</head>
<pb n="0520b" xml:id="T19.0995.0520b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0520b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b0101"><note n="0520012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">兩手當＝以兩當手【元】，（以）＋兩【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兩手當【大】，以兩當手【元】，以兩手當【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520012"><lem wit="【大】">兩手當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">以兩當手</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">以兩手當</rdg></app>心。內相叉作<note n="0520013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔拳〕－【三】</note><note n="0520013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拳【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0520013"><lem wit="【大】">拳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。並竪二大拇指誦
<lb n="0520b02" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0520b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b0301" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>爾那爾迦娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0520014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（聲）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，去聲【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520014"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">去聲</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#0520008"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0520b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b0401">不出聲誦此真言三遍。<note n="0520015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本冠註曰下皆準知四字應作細註</note>下皆准知。於頂上
<lb n="0520b05" ed="T"/>散。由結此印契誦此佛部三昧耶真言故。十
<lb n="0520b06" ed="T"/>方法界一切諸佛。悉皆雲集遍滿虛空。加持
<lb n="0520b07" ed="T"/><note n="0520016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行＋（法行）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行【大】，行法行【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520016"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">行法行</rdg></app>者離諸障惱。三業清淨所修行願速得成
<lb n="0520b08" ed="T"/>就。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520b09" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="2" type="其他">2 結諸菩薩部三昧耶印</cb:mulu><head>第二結諸菩薩部三昧耶印</head>
<lb n="0520b10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b1001">兩手當心如前作拳。左大拇指屈於掌中誦
<lb n="0520b11" ed="T"/>真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0520b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b1201" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>阿<note place="inline">引</note>嚧<note place="inline">引</note>力迦娑嚩<note place="inline">二合</note>訶<note place="inline"><note n="0520017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＋（引二）【宋】【元】，（聲引二）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，去引二【宋】【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->去聲引二【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520017"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">去引二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">去聲引二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0520b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b1301"><note n="0520018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">準＝唯【元】</note><note n="0520018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">準【大】，唯【元】</note><app n="0520018"><lem wit="【大】">準</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">唯</rdg></app>前誦三遍。於頂上散。由結此印契誦此諸
<lb n="0520b14" ed="T"/>菩薩部三昧耶真言故。即得觀自在菩薩等。
<lb n="0520b15" ed="T"/>十方法界一切菩薩。悉皆雲集遍滿虛空。加
<lb n="0520b16" ed="T"/>持行法行者三業清淨無諸災難謂諸菩薩承
<lb n="0520b17" ed="T"/>本悲願。令所求者皆悉滿足。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520b18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="3" type="其他">3 結金剛部三昧耶印</cb:mulu><head>第三結金剛部三昧耶印</head>
<lb n="0520b19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b1901">右如前印舒左大拇指。屈右大拇指於掌中。
<lb n="0520b20" ed="T"/>誦真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0520b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b2101" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>地力迦娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0520019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（引二）細註【三】＊，（二合）【甲】</note><note n="0520019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】＊，訶(引二)【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->訶二合【甲】</note><app n="0520019"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">訶<note place="inline">引二</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">訶二合</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0520b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b2201">准前誦三遍於頂上散。由結此印契誦金剛
<lb n="0520b23" ed="T"/>部三昧耶真言故。即得十方法界一切金剛
<lb n="0520b24" ed="T"/>現威怒身。如雲而集滿虛空界。加持行法行
<lb n="0520b25" ed="T"/>者。三業堅固猶如金剛。謂彼聖者承佛威神
<lb n="0520b26" ed="T"/>以自願力。大則護持國界<note n="0520020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝彼【元】</note><note n="0520020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令【大】，彼【元】</note><app n="0520020"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">彼</rdg></app>無災難。小則乃
<lb n="0520b27" ed="T"/>至一身令無諸厄。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520b28" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="4" type="其他">4 結護身印</cb:mulu><head>第四結護身印</head>
<lb n="0520b29" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520b2901">又用三部所結印契。及誦真言五處加持。謂
<pb n="0520c" xml:id="T19.0995.0520c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0520c01" ed="T"/>額左肩右肩心喉五處。於頂上散。即成被金
<lb n="0520c02" ed="T"/>剛堅固甲冑。由此加持遍行者身。威光赫<g ref="#CB03255"/>
<lb n="0520c03" ed="T"/>一切諸魔作障惱者。眼不敢覩疾走而去。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520c04" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="5" type="其他">5 結辟除印及金剛方隅寶界印</cb:mulu><head>第五結辟除印及金剛方隅寶界印</head>
<lb n="0520c05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c0501">右以前金剛部印契。誦彼真言繞壇左轉三
<lb n="0520c06" ed="T"/>匝。即能辟除大力諸魔隨佛菩薩。<note n="0520021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若有隱＝善隱顯【三】</note><note n="0520021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若有隱【大】，善隱顯【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0520021"><lem wit="【大】">若有隱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">善隱顯</rdg></app>者
<lb n="0520c07" ed="T"/>遠<note n="0520022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去字宋本白缺</note>去<note n="0520023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">他＝地【三】</note><note n="0520023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他【大】，地【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0520023"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">地</rdg></app>界。隨心大小右轉三匝。即成金剛
<lb n="0520c08" ed="T"/>方隅寶界。諸佛菩薩尚不違越。況障惱者能
<lb n="0520c09" ed="T"/>得其便。於頂上散。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520c10" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="6" type="其他">6 結請聖眾降壇印</cb:mulu><head>第六結請聖眾降壇印</head>
<lb n="0520c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c1101">右用前三部印契及誦真言。以大拇指向身
<lb n="0520c12" ed="T"/>招請。三遍三招。即前滿空三部聖眾。各依本
<lb n="0520c13" ed="T"/>位不相障礙。寂然而住頂上散。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520c14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="7" type="其他">7 獻閼伽香水印</cb:mulu><head>第七獻閼伽香水印</head>
<lb n="0520c15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c1501">右以兩手<note n="0520024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持捧＝捧持【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持捧【大】，捧持【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520024"><lem wit="【大】">持捧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">捧持</rdg></app>摩尼寶器盛香水。置於眉間
<lb n="0520c16" ed="T"/>誦真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0520c17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c1701" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>娜迦吽<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0520008"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0520c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c1801">準<note n="0520025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝前【明】【甲】</note><note n="0520025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，前【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520025"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">前</rdg></app>誦三遍。運心廣<note n="0520026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">布＝大【元】【明】</note><note n="0520026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">布【大】，大【元】【明】</note><app n="0520026"><lem wit="【大】">布</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">大</rdg></app>。次第普浴一切聖
<lb n="0520c19" ed="T"/>眾。於頂上散。由獻閼伽故。從勝解行地乃至
<lb n="0520c20" ed="T"/>法雲地。於地地中十方法界諸佛菩薩。皆悉
<lb n="0520c21" ed="T"/>加護諸<note n="0520027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔佛〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520027"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>灌<note n="0520028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">頂＋（者）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂【大】，頂者【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520028"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">頂者</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0520c22" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="8" type="其他">8 獻寶座印</cb:mulu><head>第八獻寶座印</head>
<lb n="0520c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c2301">右以兩手當心虛心合掌。二大拇指及二小
<lb n="0520c24" ed="T"/>指。相附少屈。餘之六指各散。微屈如開敷蓮
<lb n="0520c25" ed="T"/>華。<note n="0520029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（誦）ヵ＋真【甲】</note><note n="0520029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真【大】，誦真【考偽-甲】</note><app n="0520029"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">真</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="correctionRemark">誦真</rdg></app>言曰。</p>
<lb n="0520c26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c2601" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>迦磨攞娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note><app type="star" corresp="#0520019"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">訶<note place="inline">引二</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0520c27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0520c2701">由結印契及誦真言。所獻寶座令諸聖眾皆
<lb n="0520c28" ed="T"/>如實受用。則令行法行者至果位中。獲得金
<lb n="0520c29" ed="T"/>剛堅固<note n="0520030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔寶〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0520030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0520030"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>座。</p></cb:div>
<pb n="0521a" xml:id="T19.0995.0521a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0521a01" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="9" type="其他">9 結普供養印</cb:mulu><head>第九結普供養印</head>
<lb n="0521a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0521a0201">右以兩手合掌。五指互交以右<note n="0521001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">押＝壓【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0521001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">押【大】＊，壓【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0521001"><lem wit="【大】">押</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【甲】">壓</rdg></app>左。置於心
<lb n="0521a03" ed="T"/>上誦真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0521a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0521a0401" cb:type="dharani">娜莫三曼多沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>南<note place="inline"><note n="0521002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">引＋（一）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0521002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">引【大】，引一【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521002"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引一</rdg></app></note>薩嚩<note n="0521003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">他＋（引）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0521003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他【大】，他(引)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521003"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">他<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app>欠<note place="inline"><note n="0521004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">平＋（二）【宋】【元】，（聲二）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0521004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">平【大】，平二【宋】【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->平聲二【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521004"><lem wit="【大】">平</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">平二</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">平聲二</rdg></app></note>烏娜
<lb n="0521a05" ed="T"/>誐<note place="inline">二合</note>諦薩頗<note place="inline">二合</note>囉呬<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0521005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𤚥＋（三）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0521005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𤚥【大】，𤚥(三)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521005"><lem wit="【大】">𤚥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">𤚥<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app>誐誐曩<note place="inline"><note n="0521006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝二【宋】【元】</note><note n="0521006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，二【宋】【元】</note><app n="0521006"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">二</rdg></app></note>劍娑
<lb n="0521a06" ed="T"/>嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0521007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">訶＋（引四）細註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0521007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訶【大】，訶(引四)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521007"><lem wit="【大】">訶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">訶<note place="inline">引四</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0521a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0521a0701">由結此印誦真言故<note n="0521008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蓮＝運【三】【甲】</note><note n="0521008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蓮【大】，運【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521008"><lem wit="【大】">蓮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">運</rdg></app>心廣布。周遍法界諸
<lb n="0521a08" ed="T"/>佛菩薩道場海會。普雨一切諸供養具。初誦
<lb n="0521a09" ed="T"/>一遍。塵沙寶器滿盛塗香普塗聖眾。誦第二
<lb n="0521a10" ed="T"/>遍。種種花鬘普遍莊嚴。誦第三遍。燒種種香
<lb n="0521a11" ed="T"/>普遍供養。誦第四遍。雨諸天中上妙飲食。置
<lb n="0521a12" ed="T"/>於寶器普遍供養。誦第五遍。雨諸摩尼以為
<lb n="0521a13" ed="T"/>燈明普遍供養。諸佛菩薩由誦真言加持力
<lb n="0521a14" ed="T"/>故。所獻香等於諸海會悉皆真實聖眾受用。
<lb n="0521a15" ed="T"/>行法行者<note n="0521009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">於＝如【明】</note><note n="0521009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，如【明】</note><app n="0521009"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">如</rdg></app>當來世常獲是報。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0521a16" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" n="10" type="其他">10 結般若波羅蜜多根本印</cb:mulu><head>第十結般若波羅蜜多根本印</head>
<lb n="0521a17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0521a1701"><note n="0521010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">又＝當【元】【明】</note><note n="0521010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又【大】，當【元】【明】</note><app n="0521010"><lem wit="【大】">又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">當</rdg></app>以兩手背相附。收二頭指。以二小指屈於
<lb n="0521a18" ed="T"/>掌中。以大拇指各<app type="star" corresp="#0521001"><lem wit="【大】">押</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【甲】">壓</rdg></app>二指頭。置於心上。誦經
<lb n="0521a19" ed="T"/>中陀羅尼七遍。由結此印誦陀羅尼故。行法
<lb n="0521a20" ed="T"/>行者自身即便變成般若波羅蜜多菩薩。而
<lb n="0521a21" ed="T"/>為一切諸佛之母。其菩薩像結跏趺坐白蓮
<lb n="0521a22" ed="T"/>華上。身黃金色。眾寶瓔珞遍身莊嚴。首戴寶
<lb n="0521a23" ed="T"/>冠繫冠白繒。兩邊垂下。左手當心持般若梵
<lb n="0521a24" ed="T"/><note n="0521011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">夾＝筴【明】</note><note n="0521011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夾【大】，筴【明】</note><app n="0521011"><lem wit="【大】">夾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">筴</rdg></app>。右手當乳作說法印。以大拇指押無名
<lb n="0521a25" ed="T"/>指頭。即想菩薩從頂至足身諸毛孔。流出光
<lb n="0521a26" ed="T"/>明作種種色。遍滿法界。一一光中化無量佛。
<lb n="0521a27" ed="T"/>遍虛空界諸世界中。普為眾生當根宣說般
<lb n="0521a28" ed="T"/>若波羅蜜多甚深之法。皆令悟解。住三摩地
<lb n="0521a29" ed="T"/>行法行<note n="0521012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">王＝者【明】【甲】</note><note n="0521012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，者【明】【甲】</note><app n="0521012"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">者</rdg></app>作此觀已。頂上散印。手持數珠置
<pb n="0521b" xml:id="T19.0995.0521b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0521b01" ed="T"/>於掌中。合掌當心。誦真言曰。</p>
<lb n="0521b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0521b0201" cb:type="dharani"><app type="star" corresp="#0520006"><lem wit="【大】">唵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">唵<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>尾嚧者那<note place="inline">引</note>麼攞娑嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>訶<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0520008"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">引二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0521b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT19p0521b0301">誦此三遍加持數珠頂上戴已。然後當心。左
<lb n="0521b04" ed="T"/>手承珠右手移珠。念念相應住佛母三昧。觀
<lb n="0521b05" ed="T"/>心莫間斷。誦一百八遍或二十一遍。誦真言
<lb n="0521b06" ed="T"/>曰。</p>
